snippet.textDisplay: Ami ei muhurte kolkata theke bose ei gan ta sunchi. Baire bidyut chimkachche, halka bristi porche and tar sathe jhoro hawa dichche. Biswas korun sobai, eirakam prokriti-r sathe ei gan ta sunchi ami, ghor andhokar. Mone hochche satti ami padma nodir majhe bose achi chotto ekta dingi nouka te ar purnama-r chand-er akash ar nodir jol mayabi alo te bhore geche. Mon tabbhison shanto hoe gelo. Ekta advut misro potikria hochche mon-er bhitor, jeta bhasai bole bojhano sambhab noi. Asankhyo dhonnyobad coke studio-r puro team ke. Ar jini clarinet and bansi bajiechen and boga da tomake. Apnader 3 jon-er specially bolchi. Samne konodin apnader pele mati te sastange sue apnader 3 jon-er paa ta ekbar dhorte chai. Asadharan ekta masterpice. Once again arnob da ar tar puro team ke thank you erokam ekta sundor gan amader upohar dewar jonnyo. Lots of love and respect from kolkata❤❤❤❤❤❤❤🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏
